WEBVTT

1
00:13:22.340 --> 00:13:24.170
I must speak with you.

2
00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:27.800
I have received information from Earth.

3
00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:30.060
How did you manage this?

4
00:13:30.930 --> 00:13:33.600
Giving prisoners salt and pepper shakers…

5
00:13:34.810 --> 00:13:36.940
They don't know how to run a jail.

6
00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:40.320
And what is this information?

7
00:13:41.730 --> 00:13:44.780
It's not good. I'm afraid.

8
00:13:44.780 --> 00:13:48.200
Korzhenko continues to use you
to deflect his own failures.

9
00:13:49.660 --> 00:13:51.870
In the party. you are now seen as a loser

10
00:13:52.450 --> 00:13:55.540
because you failed to protect
the interests of the nation.

11
00:13:57.040 --> 00:14:01.880
I was nothing but loyal to him.
And this is how he treats me.

12
00:14:01.880 --> 00:14:04.550
And I have not gotten to the worst part.

13
00:14:05.670 --> 00:14:07.130
Your wife is under threat.

14
00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:08.680
That can't be.

15
00:14:16.270 --> 00:14:19.730
Her attempts to ensure your release

16
00:14:19.730 --> 00:14:22.150
have angered the president.

17
00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:26.530
She will publicly denounce you.

18
00:14:27.110 --> 00:14:28.820
She has no choice.

19
00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:24.090
Hello.

20
00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:28.010
My name is Natalya Polivanova

21
00:22:28.840 --> 00:22:31.220
<i>and today I am talking to you…</i>

22
00:22:31.220 --> 00:22:33.060
<i>the Soviet people.</i>

23
00:22:34.390 --> 00:22:37.230
<i>I felt it important for
the public to know the truth.</i>

24
00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:39.690
<i>My husband.</i>

25
00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:43.320
<i>Governor Leonid Polivanov.</i>

26
00:22:44.360 --> 00:22:47.780
is the one to blame for
everything that has happened on Mars.

27
00:22:51.910 --> 00:22:54.120
<i>I watched him…</i>

28
00:22:56.750 --> 00:22:58.420
ignore the problems

29
00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:01.000
until it was too late.

30
00:23:31.910 --> 00:23:33.910
<i>Those bastards…</i>

31
00:23:33.910 --> 00:23:36.410
Everything I have done for them. for him.

32
00:23:36.410 --> 00:23:38.910
and he parades my Tasha
in front of the world.

33
00:23:38.910 --> 00:23:41.000
forcing her to say those vile things.

34
00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:43.580
It is terrible. you are right.

35
00:23:43.590 --> 00:23:46.960
And under such pressure she
was still able to send me…

36
00:23:48.800 --> 00:23:52.220
Please. the people you know
in the intelligence service.

37
00:23:52.220 --> 00:23:55.100
the ones sending you information.
Can they do anything to help her?

38
00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:59.890
No. She is so closely watched
it would only make things worse.

39
00:23:59.890 --> 00:24:03.270
But you're right.
something must be done about Korzhenko.

40
00:24:03.270 --> 00:24:06.400
He is acting like a wild dog backed
into a corner. capable of anything.

41
00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:09.610
He might just destroy
the nation to save his own skin.

42
00:24:10.400 --> 00:24:11.780
Then what can be done?

43
00:24:13.490 --> 00:24:15.530
He's never been weaker in the party.

44
00:24:15.530 --> 00:24:18.240
The entire economy is
on the verge of collapse

45
00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:21.370
and with the possibility of Mars
gaining independence during his tenure.

46
00:24:21.370 --> 00:24:23.960
there is concern it could
stoke independence movements

47
00:24:23.960 --> 00:24:25.170
in parts of the Soviet empire.

48
00:24:25.170 --> 00:24:28.380
Why do you think he's trying to blame you?

49
00:24:28.380 --> 00:24:31.840
Because he knows people will blame him.

50
00:24:33.220 --> 00:24:37.890
Some people in the party. like Bolkonski.
are tired of his pseudo Stalinism.

51
00:24:37.890 --> 00:24:41.430
They want someone younger. fresher.

52
00:24:41.440 --> 00:24:44.690
Someone who can usher our
nation into the 21st century…

53
00:24:44.690 --> 00:24:46.400
someone like you.

54
00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:49.940
Are you out of your mind?
I am being held captive on another planet.

55
00:24:49.940 --> 00:24:53.570
The people see what you have
sacrificed for your nation.

56
00:24:53.570 --> 00:24:55.820
They believe in you.

57
00:24:55.820 --> 00:24:59.870
Comrade Morozova. I'm afraid
this confinement has cost you your mind.

58
00:24:59.870 --> 00:25:03.000
I have been through much worse.

59
00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.750
Korzhenko will only be able to
hold onto power another month at most.

60
00:25:05.750 --> 00:25:08.960
now that the oligarchs
have turned against him.

61
00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:11.630
It's only a matter of time.
